          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ending Taxpayer Subsidies for Yachts Act</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to deny a tax deduction for interest paid on a mortgage for a second residence of a taxpayer if that residence is a boat.</p>]]></text>
